import React from "react"; import * as userServices from "../services/userServices"; class Register extends React.Component { state = { firstName: "", latName: "", email: "", password: "", passwordConfirm: "", avatarUrl: "", }; componentDidMount() {} handleSubmit = () => { userServices .register(this.state) .then(this.onActionSuccess) .catch(this.onActionError); }; onActionSuccess = (response) => { console.log(response); }; onActionError = (err) => { console.log(err); }; render() { return (
); } } export default Register;
